LibreSubstratum is UNOFFICIAL app for Substratum Theme Engine

THIS APP REQUIRES NOUGAT ROM WITH OMS SUPPORT

NOTE: This app is not affiliate with Substratum team. Please don't post bug reports to official Substratum groups/chats.

For now this app contains only basic overlay support (compiling and enabling/disabling overlays). Setting priorities (Mix and Match from Substratum app) and support for bootanimation, sounds and wallpaper will come in next versions.

Source code: https://github.com/jereksel/LibreSubstratum

